@startuml uc-04-sequence
title UC04 — Student views personalized roadmap by selected level — Sequence
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #333333
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #333333
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #FEFEFE

actor "Student" as Student
participant "RoadmapPage" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "RoadmapService" as RoadmapService
participant "UserProfileRepository" as UserProfileRepo
participant "LevelContentRepository" as ContentRepo
participant "UserTopicProgressRepository" as ProgressRepo
participant "LangeekCrawlerJob" as Crawler
participant "Langeek Vocabulary Source" as Langeek
database "Content DB" as ContentDB
database "Content Cache" as Cache

== Scheduled content sync background context ==
Crawler -> Langeek : weekly crawl level-based topics/new words
alt Langeek reachable and crawl permitted
  Langeek -->> Crawler : A1-C2 topic/new-word pages
  Crawler -> ContentRepo : map to internal levels/topics\nand publish automatically
  ContentRepo -> ContentDB : upsert active auto-published content
  ContentRepo -> Cache : refresh active level snapshots
else Langeek down or crawl fails
  Crawler -> Cache : keep current active snapshots
  Crawler -> ContentDB : record failure/retry/log status
end

note over Crawler,ContentRepo
  Crawled content is auto-published.
  UC04 roadmap does not wait for Admin approval.
end note

== UC04 learner request ==
Student -> UI : open roadmap screen
UI -> API : GET /api/v1/roadmap
API -> RoadmapService : authorize and route user request
RoadmapService -> UserProfileRepo : get selectedLevel(userId)
UserProfileRepo -->> RoadmapService : selectedLevel = A1..C2

alt selected level exists and user is allowed
  RoadmapService -> ContentRepo : findActiveTopicsByLevel(selectedLevel)
  ContentRepo -> ContentDB : query active topics/vocabulary/activities
  ContentDB -->> ContentRepo : active content result

  alt active crawled/Admin-managed content found
    ContentRepo -->> RoadmapService : level topics and metadata
  else latest crawl failed or source unavailable
    RoadmapService -> Cache : getActiveLevelSnapshot(selectedLevel)
    Cache -->> RoadmapService : cached active topics/new words
  end

  RoadmapService -> ProgressRepo : findByUserAndLevel(userId, selectedLevel)
  ProgressRepo -->> RoadmapService : topic progress
  RoadmapService -->> API : RoadmapResponse(topics, progress, cacheStatus)
  API -->> UI : 200 OK JSON
  UI -->> Student : display selected-level roadmap
else missing selected level or unauthorized
  RoadmapService -->> API : error: login or level required
  API -->> UI : 401/403/422 JSON
  UI -->> Student : show login or level-required prompt
end
@enduml
